        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（混江龙） 遇妖猴紧追紧赶，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休得要半步相离。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨戬下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李靖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪吒！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（哪吒允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李靖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你领东南西北四渎五岳以为救应。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（混江龙） 必须要齐心努力，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "必须要歼灭渠魁。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（哪吒允，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李靖 （混江龙） 俺这里天兵天将施威武，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他那里猴卒妖兵各逞威，只杀得星斗依稀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众神同杀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李靖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好恶妖猴也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（油葫芦） 俺只见雄威赳赳勇如罴，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不枉他，不枉他号天齐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他那里奔驰一似如儿戏。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺与他一会价辨个高低。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闹垓垓几处的军声沸，恰更似平地上起个轰雷。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众神同杀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李靖 （天下乐） 只见水怪山魈尽挂铁衣，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "摇也么旗也却也助军威。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这壁厢吹觱篥，那壁厢擂鼓皮。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可也尽披靡披靡。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众神同杀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李靖 （哪吒令） 小妖们遍岭沿提奔腾一似飞。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有的妖把鼓擂。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小妖们并着腿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那山坡聚几堆。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "意欲何为，意欲何为？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鹊踏枝） 满山头天雾黑，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四下里，四下里刀枪密。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "耳边厢鬼哭神啼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只杀得紫微垣，斗转星移。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众神同杀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李靖 （胜葫芦） 这妖王法力果精奇，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不能够把他欺。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他只是三头六臂铜筋铁骨，吼一声恰似野霹雳。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众神同列阵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李靖 （幺篇） 俺只见六丁六甲显神威，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四面列层围。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他这里持剑抡枪各逞威。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一对对紧相随。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空、二郎神同入阵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀了半日，并无个对手。你且通个名儿上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨戬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妖猴听者。吾乃："
        },
        {
          "character": "杨戬",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "清源妙道二郎神，法力威灵天地闻。玉殿驰名为上将，今朝擒你泼猴狲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这些话只好哄别人，孙爷爷跟前岂是你卖弄得的？你且站稳了，听我道来："
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天地才分育吾身，参详学道拜昆仑。神通广大超三界，要上灵霄为帝君。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众神赶小猴绕场同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨戬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妖猴！你看你那些子孙都被我擒去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空看。啸天犬咬孙悟空，哪吒套。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了，罢了。杀了半日，吃了狗的亏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众天将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妖猴已擒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李靖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "诸天将，玉帝有旨，将他带领天门，请旨定夺。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大尾声） 恁只夸神通广，怎生法力精，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "准备着斩仙榜上留个名。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众神同下。）"
        }
      ],
